name: free robux generator (working 2022)
description:
PLAYING INSTRUCTIONS:

Get the present(s) to the trees before the dinosaurs catch you. Pressing space next to the present lets you pull it. You can push it without any special keys. You can press left shift to sprint and F to dash. The level is not completed until ALL presents have been secured.

WARNING:

The game may contain copyrighted music so if you're playing it on stream on in a video or anything make sure to mute the desktop audio.

The game was made with MoreMountains' Topdown Engine

Submission for Untitled Game Jam 71

We had to use some resources available online for this game
